casebody.data:
In re Carney, Vincent Laurence(MR 17209)

Lincoln, Nebraska 68507-2102

Order of the Court:

The petition by the Administrator of the Attorney Registration and Disciplinary Commission to impose reciprocal discipline pursuant to Supreme Court Rule 763 is allowed, and respondent Vincent Laurence Carney, who has been disciplined in the State of Nebraska, is reprimanded in the State of Illinois.
